b´isb´ajil tu´n t-xi nq´ama´n kye ikyjo jalin, noqtzun ayetzi´n kukx n-b´inchene. myia nim n-b´inchene.
¡Axpe ikx n-chi kyq´ama´n kyxolx Grammy ex Poppy!

Junx kyten, chʼixmi ik kyten ik tzeʼn jun ttzik ex jun ttzike. N-ximane qa ikyjo n-b´aj
aj t-xi´ya t-xu´jila jun syent ab´q´i. Kykab´il at ky-witze nim ex ky-q´ob´ extzen
ch’in ttzmal twi’ saq. Kykab´il n-chi kyq´o´n jun ky-lentes ky-q´ob´ tuk´e ky-marco te saq pwaq. Aye
kykab´il axix tok ky-chib´jel. Ex kykabʼil in che bʼisun kywitz ex in che bʼisun kywitz.

